Are you too busy to look after your dogs? Are you heading out of town and have no one to look after? 
Commercial pet hotels usually does not provide 24/7 supervision and do not have the freedom to roam around.  
 
With us, we look after your dogs in a home environment with 24/7 supervision. They also have the freedom to run around, cage-free! We usually allow the dogs to sleep with us in the bedrooms.  
 
Unfortunately, we do not accept dogs with severe anxiety issues or aggression. 
 
Owners are advised to meet us, together with their dogs, first before deciding. Food and beddings (optional) are to be provided by the owner. 
 
Daycare (per dog) 
$25/day 
 
Home Boarding Prices (based on size)  
Small dogs - $35/night 
Medium dogs - $40/night 
Large dogs - $45/night 
 
*subject to surcharges of $10/night during peak season 
*additional $25/night for each subsequent dogs 
 
We have been doing this for 3 years, with over 96 reviews (as of dec 2016) 
https://www.pawshake.com.sg/petsitters/singapore/east-chia-house-travel-no-worries-65525
